---
---

<section id="video-demo" class="bg-dark/80 py-24 px-4 border-y border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        方案<span class="text-gold">深度演示</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-gold mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        三分钟了解我们如何通过核心适配技术，为您的企业软件注入 AGI 灵魂。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative group rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 bg-black aspect-video shadow-2xl shadow-gold/5">
      <!-- Video Player -->
      <video 
        controls 
        class="w-full h-full"
        poster="/delivery_hero.png"
      >
        <source src="/人工智能赋能中小企业：解锁现有软件潜力.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        您的浏览器不支持视频播放。
      </video>
      
      <!-- Subtle overlay frame -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none border-[12px] border-white/5 rounded-2xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 flex justify-center">
       <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-gold">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white font-bold text-sm italic">“看见” 确定性的连接力量</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs text-left">演示内容：Legacy 系统到 Agent-Native 的跨越</p>
          </div>
       </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
